Mon Oct 10 16:27:57 CEST 2016
        Implementing:
        - /track API, to map transactions to wire transfers and
        viceversa.
        - /history API, to get the list of transactions in DB.
        - merchant "instances", to run make multiple shops on the
        same backend.
